This project must have one canonical AI architecture.

Rules:
- Do not create new parallel AI service trees.
- Before changing AI code, verify whether logic belongs to:
  - canonical AI service package
  - repository layer
  - provider layer
  - policy layer
- Prefer consolidation over duplication.
- If a module is legacy, add adapter/deprecation path instead of copying logic.
- FAQ access must use a single canonical repository contract.